(32, 'Lanka and Leopard', 'lanka-and-leopard', '15', 7, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 25%', 12453, 4578, 'Colombo', 'Bentota', 'Colombo-Kandy-Nuwara Eliya-Yala-Bentota-Colombo', '', '<p>Marco Polo considered Sri Lanka &ldquo;the finest island of its size in the world&rdquo;. We invite you to explore this superb destination with this small tour which covers some ancient cities and UNESCO World Heritage Sites, spice coast, tea states and finishing your holiday with spotting leopards amongst many other wild animals, reptiles and birds in Yala national ark.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>&middot; Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in 1400hrs /Out 1200hrs in Comfort, Deluxe &amp; Luxury hotels)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Private air-condition Car with English speaking Chauffeur guide for travel &amp; transfers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meals as motioned above. (B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Temple of the Tooth Relic</li>\r\n	<li>Cultural show at Kandy</li>\r\n	<li>Tea plantation / factory visit</li>\r\n	<li>Yala National park safari &ndash; 01 jeep hire</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&middot; Meet and greet at the airport by THO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; All current applicable taxes</p>\r\n', '', 'Untitled_design_-_2019-04-22T142149_297.jpg', 'sri lanka tour,travel tourism', 'Untitled_design_-_2019-04-22T142711_775.jpg', 'sri lanka tour,total holiday options', 'cave1.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '33,34,36', '2019-04-22 14:29:58', '2019-04-26 13:49:47'),
(33, 'Lanka Explorer', 'lanka-explorer', '16', 18, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 20%', 1245, 4578, 'Colombo', 'Ambalangoda', 'Colombo-Negombo-Anuradhapura-Jaffna-Habarana-Kandy-Nuwara Eliya-Yala-Galle-Ambalangoda-Colombo', '', '<p>We call Sri Lanka Paradise and still people do use the same name to describe the country because of its landscapes, beaches, mountains, food, festivals and its hospitality. To explore more this wonderful island and experience untouched destinations and uniqueness of the county this tour will suit for the ones who is exactly looking for memorable and relaxed experience. Some of the newly introduce destinations such as Jaffna included to the tour with splendour beach stay with covering all major highlights of Sri Lanka.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>&middot;&nbsp; Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in/Out 1200hrs in Comfort &amp; Deluxe hotels)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp; Private air-condition Car/van (04 pax) with English speaking Chauffeur guide for travel &amp; transfers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp; Meals as motioned above. (B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp; &nbsp;Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Anuradhapura</li>\r\n	<li>Isurumuniya</li>\r\n	<li>Mihintale</li>\r\n	<li>Cultural Show</li>\r\n	<li>Peradeniya Botanical Gardens</li>\r\n	<li>Temple of the Tooth Relic</li>\r\n	<li>Polonnaruwa</li>\r\n	<li>Dambulla cave temple</li>\r\n	<li>Sigiriya</li>\r\n	<li>Sri Maha Bodhi Tree</li>\r\n	<li>Minneriya National Park with jeep</li>\r\n	<li>Yala National Park with jeep</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp; &nbsp;Meet and greet at the airport by THO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp; &nbsp;All current applicable taxes</p>\r\n', '', 'colombo.jpg', 'sri lanka tour,travel', 'sygiria.jpg', 'best of sri lanka,sri lanka tour', 'colombo-city1.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '27,28,29', '2019-04-22 14:54:27', '2019-04-26 13:50:18'),
(34, 'Panoramic Lanka', 'panoramic-lanka', '15', 13, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 35%', 1245, 4578, 'Colombo', 'Anuradhapura', 'Colombo-Yala-Nuwara Eliya-Kandy-Matale-Trincomalee-Sigiriya-Hiriwadunna-Dambulla-Anuradhapura-Colombo', '', '<p>Marco Polo considered Sri Lanka &ldquo;the finest island of its size in the world&rdquo;. We invite you to explore this superb destination, visiting the ancient cities and UNESCO World Heritage Sites of Anuradhapura, Polonnaruwa, Sigiriya and Dambulla. Relive the days of the British Raj in the evocative hill station of Nuwara Eliya, set in wonderful mountain scenery amidst tea plantations. Also be one of the first to visit the eastern coast at Trincomalee. This splendid itinerary includes some easy trekking, nature safaris and excellent all-round introduction to Sri Lanka.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>&middot; Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in 1400hrs /Out 1200hrs in Comfort, Deluxe &amp; Luxury hotels)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Private air-condition Car/Van (4pax) with English speaking Chauffeur guide for travel &amp; transfers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meals as motioned above. (B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Anuradhapura sacred city sightseeing</li>\r\n	<li>Polonnaruwa sacred city sightseeing</li>\r\n	<li>Minneriya National park &ndash; 01 Jeep hire</li>\r\n	<li>Hiriwadunna Village excursion</li>\r\n	<li>Dambulla cave temple</li>\r\n	<li>Sigiriya Rock fortress</li>\r\n	<li>Trincomalee sightseeing</li>\r\n	<li>Temple of the Tooth Relic</li>\r\n	<li>Cultural show</li>\r\n	<li>Peradeniya Royal Botanical garden</li>\r\n	<li>Yala National Park &ndash; 01 jeep hire</li>\r\n	<li>Galle city sightseeing</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &middot; Meet and greet at the airport by THO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &middot; All current applicable taxes</p>\r\n', '', 'golden_temple.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'ColomboCityWalkingTour.jpg', 'best of sri lanka', 'fisherman1.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '32,35,37', '2019-04-22 15:15:25', '2019-04-26 13:50:35'),
(35, 'Secrets of Lanka', 'secrets-of-lanka', '15', 14, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 45%', 1245, 4578, 'Colombo', 'Tangalle', 'Colombo-Anuradhapura-Polonnaruwa-Sigiriya-Minneriya-Kandy-Nuwara Eliya-Yala-Galle-Tangalle-Colombo Departure', '', '<p>This in-depth tour encompasses all the major sites of the Cultural Triangle before taking a leisurely route through the centre and south visiting temples, tea plantations and a national park to reach one of the glorious beaches that stretches the length of the southwest coast. Highlights of the north include Anuradhapura, 4th century BC cradle of Buddhism, the exquisite carved rock Buddha images at Polonnaruwa and Kandy with its wonderful Peradeniya Botanical Gardens and the Temple of the Tooth.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCarry on up to the High Country to relax on a charming tea plantation before going to the elephant and leopard filled Yala National Park located in the southeast. Follow the coast and explore the fort in Galle, then head north to beautiful beaches of northern Galle where you can relax and soak in the Sri Lankan sun.</p>\r\n', '<p>Any International airfare not mentioned and Visa fee, Early check in or late check out,&nbsp;Meals other than specified above, Tips &amp; Gratuities, Travel &amp; Medical Insurance, Camera and video permits, Expenses incurred due to flight / train cancellation or delay, Any expense of a personal nature, like drinks, laundry, telephone calls, mini bar, etc, any optional excursion or tour, any other expense not mentioned in the prices include column Entry Visa Fees, please visit <a href=\"http://www.eta.gov.lk/\">www.eta.gov.lk</a> for more details / submit your individual visa application.</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Hotel accommodation with private facilities (Check out 1200hrs/ Check-in 1400hrs)</li>\r\n	<li>Travel by chartered air-conditioned <strong>chauffeu</strong>r vehicle</li>\r\n	<li>Meals as specified <strong>(B=Breakfast=D=Dinner)</s