(36, 'Spirit of Lanka', 'spirit-of-lanka', '15', 12, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 25%', 1245, 4578, 'Colombo', 'Beruwala', 'Colombo-Dambulla-Polonnaruwa-Minneriya-Kandy-Nuwara Eliya-Horton Plains-Beruwala-Gale Fort-Colombo', '', '<p>Marco Polo considered Sri Lanka &ldquo;the finest island of its size in the world&rdquo;. We invite you to explore this superb destination, visiting the ancient cities and UNESCO World Heritage Sites of Sigiriya and Dambulla. Travel to the bustling city of Kandy where you may explore the Temple of the Tooth Relic and the magnificent Peredeniya Botanical Gardens. Travel to Nuwara Eliya and enjoy the misty experience of the tea garden. Finishing your holiday with spotting leopards amongst many other wild animals, reptiles and birds in Yala national park and with splendour beach stay with covering all major highlights of Sri Lanka.</p>\r\n', '', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in 1400hrs /Out 1200hrs in, Deluxe &amp; Luxury hotels)&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Individual Arrival Transfer for each pax for the SOLO TOUR(Arrival Transfer only, fixed departure transfer based on shared coach for entire group)</li>\r\n	<li>Private air-condition Transportation as below\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li>1-2 Pax &ndash; A/C car with English speaking chauffeur guide</li>\r\n		<li>3-6Pax &ndash; A/C Van with English speaking chauffeur guide</li>\r\n		<li>7 &ndash; 11 Pax &ndash; A/C Mini coach with English Speaking National Guide</li>\r\n		<li>12 &ndash; 20 Pax &ndash; A/C coach with English speaking National Guide</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Meals as motioned above. <strong>(B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</strong></li>\r\n	<li>High Tea in Grand Hotel Nuwara Eliya</li>\r\n	<li>Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:\r\n	<ul style=\"list-style-type:circle\">\r\n		<li>Colombo City tour in Tuk Tuk</li>\r\n		<li>Dambulla Cave Temples</li>\r\n		<li>Polonnaruwa Sightseeing</li>\r\n		<li>Minneriya National Park</li>\r\n		<li>Sigiriya Rock Fortress</li>\r\n		<li>Visit to a Spice Garden</li>\r\n		<li>Temple of Sacred Tooth Relic</li>\r\n		<li>Sightseeing in Kandy</li>\r\n		<li>Peradeniya Royal Botanical Gardens</li>\r\n		<li>Visit to a Tea Factory</li>\r\n		<li>Horton Plains Trekking</li>\r\n		<li>Galle City tour</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Meet and greet at the airport by THO</li>\r\n	<li>All current applicable taxes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'sri-lanka-elephant-inn1.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'Hiriwadunna1.jpg', 'best of sri lanka tour', 'srch2.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '28,29,33', '2019-04-22 16:36:50', '2019-04-26 14:56:10'),
(37, 'Wildlife Wonders of Lanka', 'wildlife-wonders-of-lanka', '15', 10, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 55%', 1244, 4577, 'Colombo', 'Negombo', 'Colombo-Negombo-Sinharaja-Udawalawe-Bundala-Yala-Nuwara Eliya-Horton Plains & Kandy-Knuckles-Wasgamuwa-Negombo-Colombo', '', '<p>Wildlife of Sri Lanka is very unique, though it&rsquo;s very small country but offer Sri Lanka is ranked amongst the world&rsquo;s twenty five biodiversity hot spots. As a country with high rate of endemism it has many faunal groups including birds, mammals, reptiles, amphibians and renowned as one of the best places to watch Asiatic elephants and leopards for nature enthusiastic and photographers. Safaris are arranged with cultural tours as it is possible to find wide range of wildlife in place surrounded by cultural heritages mainly in the dry zone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the key reasons which makes Sri Lanka a popular wild life destination is the availability of expertise. This tour covers variety of national parks to ensuring you get the chance to see all possible wildlife exists in the country.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>&middot; Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in 1400hrs /Out 1200hrs in Comfort, Deluxe &amp; Luxury hotels)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Private air-condition Car / Van (04 pax) with English speaking Chauffeur guide for travel &amp; transfers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meals as motioned above. (B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Sinharaja Rainforest Visit</li>\r\n	<li>Udawalawe National Park Safari</li>\r\n	<li>Bundala National Park Visit</li>\r\n	<li>Yala National park &ndash; 02 Safari&rsquo;s</li>\r\n	<li>Tea plantation</li>\r\n	<li>Horton Plains National Park</li>\r\n	<li>Temple of the Tooth Relic</li>\r\n	<li>Cultural show</li>\r\n	<li>Knuckles valley</li>\r\n	<li>Wasgamuwa National park</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meet and greet at the airport by THO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; All current applicable taxes</p>\r\n', '', 'Glimpse_of_Paradise1.jpg', 'best of sri lanka', 'Tri_Nation_Tour_Kalutara_-_Tea_Gardens.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'little-monks1.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '29,32,33', '2019-04-22 16:50:01', '2019-04-26 14:55:52'),
(39, 'Flavours of Lanka Village Cooking Class', 'flavours-of-lanka-village-cooking-class', '17', 1, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Best short tour to refresh', 'Upto 15%', 15000, 24999, 'Sri Lanka', 'Sri Lanka', 'Local Place', '', '', '', '', '', 'sri-lanka_colombo_cooking-class_food.jpg', 'Sri lanka short tour,sri lanka tour', 'Flavours_of_Lanka_Village_Cooking_Class.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'srch5.jpg', 'best food of sri lanka', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '27,33,34', '2019-04-25 16:59:12', '2019-04-26 14:54:38'),
(40, 'Best of Ceylon', 'best-of-ceylon', '15', 11, '2019-04-01', '2019-12-31', 'Get the best travel deal of all time!', 'Upto 25%', 1242, 4512, 'Colombo', 'Bentota', 'Colombo-Dambulla-Kandy-Nuwara Eliya-Bentota-Colombo', '', '<p>This brief tour combines culture and relaxation taking in some of Sri Lanka&rsquo;s finest historical, archaeological and natural treasures whilst not forgetting the pleasures of a few days by the sea. Tour the &lsquo;Cultural Triangle&rsquo; visiting the ancient cities of Polonnaruwa and Anarudhapura, the sacred cave temple of Dambulla and the inspiring sky citadel of Sigiriya. Travel to the bustling city of Kandy where you may explore the Temple of the Tooth Relic and the magnificent Peredeniya Botanical Gardens. Travel to Nuwara Eliya and enjoy the misty experience of the tea garden. Finish the trip with a few days at a charming boutique hotel with miles of beaches right at your doorstep.</p>\r\n', '', '<p>&middot; Accommodation in hotel with private facility (Check in 1400hrs /Out 1200hrs in Comfort, Deluxe &amp; Luxury hotels)&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Private air-condition Car (02 pax) / Van (04 pax) with English speaking Chauffeur guide for travel &amp; transfers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meals as motioned above. (B= Breakfast, D=Dinner)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Entry tickets to the monuments/ sights as below:</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Dambulla cave temple</li>\r\n	<li>Anuradhapura sacred city sightseeing</li>\r\n	<li>Mihintale premises</li>\r\n	<li>Catamaran ride at Lake Habarana</li>\r\n	<li>Polonnaruwa sacred city sightseeing</li>\r\n	<li>Minneriya National Park 01 Jeep hire</li>\r\n	<li>Sigiriya rock fortress</li>\r\n	<li>Temple of the Tooth Relic</li>\r\n	<li>Cultural show</li>\r\n	<li>Peradeniya Royal Botanical garden</li>\r\n	<li>Tea plantation / factory visit</li>\r\n	<li>Horton Plains National park visit</li>\r\n	<li>Galle city tour</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; Meet and greet at the airport by THO</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&middot; All current applicable taxes</p>\r\n', '', 'tea-plant2.jpg', 'best of ceylon,sri lanka tour', 'tea-plant3.jpg', 'sri lanka tour', 'srch6.jpg', 'sri lanka,sri lanka tour', 'accommodation-Transport-Sightseeing', '27,34,35', '2019-04-25 17:37:02', '2019-04-26 14:54:08');

